    • Method Detail

      • GetConfigurations

        @BusMethod(signature="s",
           replySignature="a{sv}")
java.util.Map<java.lang.String,org.alljoyn.bus.Variant> GetConfigurations(java.lang.String languageTag)
                                                                          throws org.alljoyn.bus.BusException
        Get the writable properties of the device.
        Parameters:
        languageTag - IETF language tags specified by RFC 5646
        Returns:
        Return all the updatable configuration fields based on the language tag. See The list of known configuration fields for more details. If language tag is not specified (i.e. ""), configuration fields based on device's language preference are returned.
        Throws:
        org.alljoyn.bus.BusException

      • FactoryReset

        @BusMethod
@BusAnnotations(value=@BusAnnotation(name="org.freedesktop.DBus.Method.NoReply",value="true"))
void FactoryReset()
                  throws org.alljoyn.bus.BusException
        Direct the device to disconnect from the personal AP, clear all previously configured data, and start the soft AP mode. Some device may not support this feature. In such a case, the AllJoyn error code org.alljoyn.Error.FeatureNotAvailable will be returned in the AllJoyn response.
        Throws:
        org.alljoyn.bus.BusException
